The paper discusses secure learning algorithms for on-device learning networks, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG) and security and privacy (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the use of parallel computing, which falls under distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper discusses the vulnerability of the networks to Byzantine adversaries, which is related to system and control theory (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses future research directions, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
